  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Your Turn][Once Per Turn] When a card is removed from
    your opponent''s security stack, you may activate 1 of this Digimon''s [On Deletion]
    effects.[On Deletion] You may play 1 red Digimon with [Avian], [Bird], [Beast],
    [Animal], or [Sovereign] in one of its traits and 3000 DP or less from your hand
    without paying the cost. For each red Tamer you have in play, add 2000 to the
    maximum DP of the card you can play by this effect.'
